1
00:00:09,494 --> 00:00:11,728
Chalk in the pocket.

2
00:00:11,728 --> 00:00:13,962
Door in the dusk.

3
00:00:13,962 --> 00:00:16,277
Hinge like a heartbeat.

4
00:00:16,277 --> 00:00:26,538
Latch learning trust.

5
00:00:26,888 --> 00:00:29,920
I draw a quiet circle where the doorway breathes,

6
00:00:29,920 --> 00:00:32,154
thin white grammar where the night unweaves.

7
00:00:32,154 --> 00:00:34,308
Corners remember the curve of the hand,

8
00:00:34,308 --> 00:00:36,222
sigils like snowfall that chooses to land.

9
00:00:36,222 --> 00:00:38,856
I mark for arrivals who come without sound,

10
00:00:38,856 --> 00:00:41,011
for weary returning who want common ground.

11
00:00:41,011 --> 00:00:43,484
The stone takes a symbol and offers it rest,

12
00:00:43,484 --> 00:00:54,543
chalk dust answers like milk on a chest.

13
00:00:54,893 --> 00:00:57,048
Open for luck with a soft white key,

14
00:00:57,048 --> 00:00:59,362
close upon harm but not upon sea.

15
00:00:59,362 --> 00:01:01,515
Welcome returns that carry no blade,

16
00:01:01,515 --> 00:01:12,415
grant passing to peace by the sign I made.

17
00:01:12,766 --> 00:01:15,239
I write small types for a tender art,

18
00:01:15,239 --> 00:01:17,472
what holds a hand and what holds a heart.

19
00:01:17,472 --> 00:01:19,947
List of kind looks, set of warm names,

20
00:01:19,947 --> 00:01:22,180
record of promises, fields without blame.

21
00:01:22,180 --> 00:01:24,415
Optional sorrow with reason attached,

22
00:01:24,415 --> 00:01:26,728
union of stories not perfectly matched.

23
00:01:26,728 --> 00:01:29,043
Pointer to patience, reference to grace,

24
00:01:29,043 --> 00:01:40,262
stack of small moments kept near this place.

25
00:01:40,611 --> 00:01:42,846
Route for the tired, query for calm,

26
00:01:42,846 --> 00:01:45,079
token is kindness, header is balm.

27
00:01:45,079 --> 00:01:47,313
GET a night’s breathing, POST your return,

28
00:01:47,313 --> 00:02:25,661
cache a safe hour while ember-lights burn.

29
00:02:26,010 --> 00:02:28,403
I chalk for the wanderer crossing the rain,

30
00:02:28,403 --> 00:02:30,558
for keys that forget and remember again.

31
00:02:30,558 --> 00:02:33,032
For shoes full of gravel and pockets of leaves,

32
00:02:33,032 --> 00:02:35,026
for mouths that were quiet and now want to speak.

33
00:02:35,026 --> 00:02:37,899
I scribe little runes where the splinters begin,

34
00:02:37,899 --> 00:02:40,133
whiten the wound so the daylight can win.

35
00:02:40,133 --> 00:02:44,282
Doorframe listens. The grain takes note.

36
00:02:44,282 --> 00:02:56,139
Words turn simple inside the throat.

37
00:02:56,489 --> 00:02:58,644
Bind what is scattered, free what is tight,

38
00:02:58,644 --> 00:03:00,877
rate-limit worry, throttle the night.

39
00:03:00,877 --> 00:03:03,270
Handshake of welcome, semaphore green,

40
00:03:03,270 --> 00:03:04,836
enter and loosen the weathered machine.

41
00:03:05,186 --> 00:03:08,058
Love is a datatype older than fire,

42
00:03:08,058 --> 00:03:10,293
sum of the small and the steady desire.

43
00:03:10,293 --> 00:03:12,447
Product of holding and giving away,

44
00:03:12,447 --> 00:03:15,000
keys to the room where the rough edges stay.

45
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:17,234
Schema migrates as the seasons revise,

46
00:03:17,234 --> 00:03:19,388
fields gain meaning when looked at with eyes.

47
00:03:19,388 --> 00:03:21,941
I chalk it in cursive too soft to declare,

48
00:03:21,941 --> 00:03:28,612
syntax of mercy the door can bear.

49
00:03:28,962 --> 00:03:31,276
Grant for the meek, deny to the blade,

50
00:03:31,276 --> 00:03:33,510
route us to home when our courage is frayed.

51
00:03:33,510 --> 00:03:35,425
Return with a body of linen and light,

52
00:03:35,425 --> 00:03:43,852
status code tender, all quiet, all right.

53
00:03:44,201 --> 00:03:46,515
Chalk in the pocket.

54
00:03:46,515 --> 00:03:48,830
Door in the day.

55
00:03:48,830 --> 00:03:52,260
Threshold remembers.

56
00:03:52,260 --> 00:03:54,495
You may.
